#. <section class="sutta" id="sn47.45"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn47.45:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 47"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 47"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn47.45:0.2"
msgid "5. Amatavagga"
msgstr "5. The Deathless"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn47.45:0.3"
msgid "45. Kusalarāsisutta"
msgstr "45. A Heap of the Skillful"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn47.45:1.1"
msgid ""
"“‘Kusalarāsī’ti, bhikkhave, vadamāno cattāro satipaṭṭhāne sammā vadamāno "
"vadeyya."
msgstr ""
"“Rightly speaking, mendicants, you’d call these four kinds of mindfulness "
"meditation a ‘heap of the skillful’."

msgctxt "sn47.45:1.2"
msgid "Kevalo hāyaṃ, bhikkhave, kusalarāsi, yadidaṃ—cattāro satipaṭṭhānā."
msgstr ""
"For these four kinds of mindfulness meditation are entirely a heap of the "
"skillful."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pli5.187"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn47.45:2.1"
msgid "Katame cattāro?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "sn47.45:2.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu kāye kāyānupassī viharati ātāpī sampajāno satimā, "
"vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ;"
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant meditates by observing an aspect of the body—keen, "
"aware, and mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the world."

msgctxt "sn47.45:2.3"
msgid "vedanāsu … pe …"
msgstr "They meditate observing an aspect of feelings …"

msgctxt "sn47.45:2.4"
msgid "citte … pe …"
msgstr "mind …"

msgctxt "sn47.45:2.5"
msgid ""
"dhammesu dhammānupassī viharati ātāpī sampajāno satimā, vineyya loke "
"abhijjhādomanassaṃ."
msgstr ""
"principles—keen, aware, and mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the "
"world."

msgctxt "sn47.45:2.6"
msgid ""
"‘Kusalarāsī’ti, bhikkhave, vadamāno ime cattāro satipaṭṭhāne sammā vadamāno "
"vadeyya."
msgstr ""
"Rightly speaking, you’d call these four kinds of mindfulness meditation a ‘"
"heap of the skillful’."

msgctxt "sn47.45:2.7"
msgid "Kevalo hāyaṃ, bhikkhave, kusalarāsi, yadidaṃ—cattāro satipaṭṭhānā”ti."
msgstr ""
"For these four kinds of mindfulness meditation are entirely a heap of the "
"skillful.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn47.45:2.8"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ."
msgstr ""
